{"tid":2512231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我喺百幾個無宣誓既公務員 講少少公務員既現實","createTime":"2021-05-01T13:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T13:52:49.000Z","uid":196546,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b407cba8de85214dd94514bc9065848ac64fd51","tid":2512231,"uid":196546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:48:25.000Z","msg":"(召集)將會拒絕宣誓既公務員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2322503\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2322503</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX9EWDdgUZNs6bVkwT63wEtUVgw7XBEhuQCiDhkU8P2hb?filename=pjykW2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjykW2v.jpg&h=705bfc8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1) 公務員黃藍比例大約是5:5<br />\n隨年齡層不同, 比例亦加減調整, 但絕對有年輕喺藍.<br />\n2) 大部分公務員都喺無專業技能<br />\n因此喺市場上揾唔番相同人工既工作, 再引伸而只有百幾個無宣誓<br />\n相信無宣誓公務員大部分都會移民/有能力喺私人市場工作<br />\n3) 有離職潮, 但規模唔大<br />\n分水嶺在於舊制同新制公務員退休福利既分別, 舊制有長糧等福利,<br />\n所以離職/無宣誓公務員主要都喺新制<br />\n4) 黃公務員留低原因<br />\n有家庭既, 希望捱到子女出國讀書,唔介意做太空人.<br />\n無負擔既, 除非職業非常特殊, 否則盡快揾夠離開政府.<br />\n所以依家就算強制留低既黃公務員去打疫苗, 大部分都會去打, 目標只喺鬥長命<br />\n5) 無改變體制既想法<br />\n唔好幻想政府內部有一個有英雄人物出現, 未來會推翻整個公務員體制.<br />\n6) 黃公務員爭扎求存<br />\n有唔少黃公務員喺今次反修例中盡最大努力付出, 做家長車, 提供資料...<br />\n當中有人被炒, 被拘捕過, 甚至坐監. <br />\n其他黃公務員可能做到既就只有堅持食黃店, 捐錢比612<br />\n或者會比連登仔批鬥, 但已經係佢地做到最大既事"},{"pid":"a50712d10ccd77325f51a94641fa051540da859c","tid":2512231,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31415138884a7dc5d0a7bbbb0194e047310b8b07","tid":2512231,"uid":360820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"如果有idea可以一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[拋磚] 第一屆許智峯訪問節目改名大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2512221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2512221</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2ed714e77433e2e201c10b5adb2f98e8fadbfe2","tid":2512231,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb09869dccef03073bacccc01bccc2928fbe646","tid":2512231,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}